<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>진료 예약 선택 - MediCare+</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <script src="/js/feather.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col">
  {{> common/header-public}}
  
  <main class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-8">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-12 relative">
        <button onclick="location.href='/'" class="absolute top-0 left-0 flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-800 font-medium">
          <i data-feather="arrow-left" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
          처음으로
        </button>

        <div class="text-center mb-12 mt-8">
          <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">진료 예약</h1>
          <p class="text-slate-500">원하시는 예약 방식을 선택해주세요.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 w-full max-w-4xl">
          <button onclick="location.href='/reservation/symptom-reservation'" class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-md hover:border-indigo-300 transition-all group flex flex-col items-center text-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-indigo-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600 mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <i data-feather="activity" class="w-10 h-10"></i>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">AI 증상 추천 예약</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
              어디가 아픈지 증상을 입력하시면<br/>
              AI가 적합한 진료과와 전문의를 추천해 드립니다.
            </p>
          </button>

          <button onclick="location.href='/reservation/direct-reservation'" class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-md hover:border-indigo-300 transition-all group flex flex-col items-center text-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600 mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <i data-feather="calendar" class="w-10 h-10"></i>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">직접 선택 예약</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
              원하시는 진료과와 전문의,<br/>
              예약 시간을 직접 선택하여 예약합니다.
            </p>
          </button>

          <button onclick="location.href='/reservation/lookup'" class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-md hover:border-indigo-300 transition-all group flex flex-col items-center text-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-green-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-green-600 mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <i data-feather="search" class="w-10 h-10"></i>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">예약 조회</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
              예약번호 또는 이름과 전화번호로<br/>
              기존 예약을 조회하고 변경·취소합니다.
            </p>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  {{> common/footer-public}}
  <script>
    feather.replace();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
